zabbix_export:
  version: '7.4'
  host_groups:
    - uuid: 2c129769852c4c1b879bbad47dcf97cf
      name: Test
  hosts:
    - host: TEST
      name: TEST
      description: |
        To reproduce the problem, type in the terminal.
        
        Для вызова проблемы написать в терминале 
        
        zabbix_sender -z 127.0.0.1 -s "TEST" -k test.alert -o 1
        
        To solve the problem, change 1 to 0.
        
        Для решения проблемы изменить 1 на 0
        
        zabbix_sender -z 127.0.0.1 -s "TEST" -k test.alert -o 0
      groups:
        - name: Test
      items:
        - name: 'Test alert'
          type: TRAP
          key: test.alert
          triggers:
            - expression: last(/TEST/test.alert)=1
              name: 'Test alert trigger'
              priority: AVERAGE
